ness and the most excellent reward, and raise him to the praiseworthy\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25703,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/29\/repeat-adhan-then-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":34448,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Adhan: Repeat the call to prayer, then supplicate","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 29, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, the callers to prayer have been favored over us.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSay as they have said. When you have finished, ask Allah and you will receive.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34446,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/05\/dua-forgiveness-adhan\/","url_meta":{"origin":34448,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Adhan: Supplication for forgiveness after call to prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d ibn Abi Waqqas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever says when he hears the call to prayer, \u2018I testify there is no God but Allah alone, without any partner, and Muhammad is His servant and His messenger, I am pleased with Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&q